--
-- PARAMETERS:
--      geoRaster        - Source SDO_GEORASTER object
--      pyramidLevel     - The pyramid level of the returned resolution,
--                         default to the pyramid level 0.
--      SRID             - The SRID for the returned resolution, default to the
